All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Baker
A `Baker` represents an employee of a `Pizzeria` who cooks pizzas.
Config
A `Config` represents the configuration settings for a pizzeria.
Courier
A `Courier` represents an employee of a pizzeria who is responsible for delivering pizzas to customers.
Customer
A `Customer` represents a customer who wants to order a pizza from a `Pizzeria`.
Main
This class represents the entry point of the pizza delivery simulation program.
Order
Represents an order of a pizza.
OrderState
An enumeration representing the different states an order can be in: QUEUED, COOKING, COOKED, WAREHOUSE, DELIVERING, and DELIVERED.
Pizza
The Pizza class represents a pizza object.
Pizzeria
The Pizzeria class represents a pizzeria where orders can be made and fulfilled.
Warehouse
A warehouse class that stores pizza orders until they are picked up by couriers for delivery.
